\c 3
\p '
\v 1 Ipapo akati kwandiri, Mwanakomana womunhu, chidya chaunowana; chidya rugwaro urwu rwakapetwa uende, undotaura neimba yaIsiraeri.
\p
\v 2 Ipapo ndakashamisa muromo wangu, iye akandidyisa rugwaro rwakapetwa.
\v 3 Akati kwandiri, Mwanakomana womunhu, dyisa dumbu rako, ugutise vura bwako norugwaro rwakapetwa urwu rwandinokupa. Ipapo ndikarudya, rukava mumukamwa wangu sohuchi nokuzipa.
\p
\v 4 Zvino akati kwandiri, Mwanakomana womunhu, famba uende kuimba yaIsiraeri, utaure kwavari mashoko angu.
\p
\v 5 Nokuti hautumwi kurudzi runo mutauriro usingazikamwi norurimi rwakaoma, asi kuimba yaIsiraeri;
\v 6 hautumwi kumarudzi mazhinji anomutauriro usingazikamwi norurimi rwakaoma, vausingagoni kunzwisisa mashoko avo. Zvirokwazvo, dai ndaikutuma kwavari vangadai vaikunzwa.
\v 7 Asi imba yaIsiraeri icharamba kukunzwa, nokuti havadi kundinzwa ini, nokuti imba yose yaIsiraeri vane huma dzakaoma, nomoyo mikukutu.
\v 8 Tarira, ndinoomesa chiso chako sezvakaita zviso zvavo, nehuma yako sezvakaita huma dzavo.
\v 9 Ndakaomesa huma yako sedhaimani rinokunda musarasara; usavatya, usavhunduswa nezviso zvavo, nokuti ivo iimba inondimukira simba.
\p
\v 10 Akatiwo kwandiri, Mwanakomana womunhu, mashoko angu ose andichataura kwauri, uagamuchire mumoyo mako, uanzwe nenzeve dzako.
\v 11 Famba uende kuna vari mukutapwa, kuvana vavanhu vako, utaure navo uvaudze uti, `Ndizvo zvinotaura Ishe Jehovha, kana vachida kunzwa, kana vasingadi.'
\p
\v 12 Ipapo Mweya wakandisimudza, ndikanzwa shure kwangu mubvumo wokuunga kukuru, zvichiti, Kubwinya kwaJehovha ngakurumbidzwe panzvimbo yake.
\v 13 Ndikanzwa mubvumo wamapapiro ezvipenyu, achigunzvana, nomubvumo wamakumbo engoro kumativi azvo, uri mubvumo wokuunga kukuru.
\p
\v 14 Ipapo Mweya wakandisimudza, ndokundibvisapo; ndikaenda ndine shungu, mweya wangu wakatsamwa; ruoko rwaJehovha rwakanga ruri pamusoro pangu nesimba.
\v 15 Zvino ndakasvika kuna vaiva mukutapwa paTeriabhibhi, vakanga vagere parwizi rwaKebhari, ipapo pavakanga vagere; ini ndikagarapo pakati pavo mazuva manomwe ndichishayiwa mashoko.
\s Ezekieri anodamwa ave nharirire yaIsiraeri
\p
\v 16 Zvino mazuva manomwe akati apera, shoko raJehovha rikasvika kwandiri richiti,
\p
\v 17 Mwanakomana womunhu, ndakakuita nharire yeimba yaIsiraeri; naizvozvo chinzwa shoko rinobva mumuromo mangu, uvanyevere panzvimbo yangu.
\p
\v 18 Kana ini ndikati kuno wakaipa, `Zvirokwazvo uchafa,' iwe ukasamunyevera, kana kutaura zvinonyevera wakaipa panzira yake yakaipa, kuti aponese upenyu hwake, munhu uyu wakaipa achafira muzvakaipa zvake, asi ropa rake ndicharibvunza paruoko rwako.
\v 19 Asi kana iwe ukanyevera akaipa, akasatendeuka pazvakaipa zvake, kana panzira yake yakaipa, iye achafira muzvakaipa zvake, asi iwe waponesa hako mweya wako.
\p
\v 20 Uyezve, kana munhu akarurama akatsauka pakururama kwake, akaita zvakaipa, ini ndikaisa chigumbuso pamberi pake, achafa; zvausina kumunyevera, achafira muzvivi zvake; zvakarurama zvaakaita hazvingarangarirwi, asi ropa rake ndicharibvunza paruoko rwako.
\p
\v 21 Asi kana ukanyevera munhu wakarurama, kuti wakarurama arege kutadza, iye akasatadza, zvirokwazvo achararama, nokuti wakateerera kunyeverwa, newe waponesa mweya wako.
\p
\v 22 Ruoko rwaJehovha rwakanga ruri pamusoro pangu ipapo, akati kwandiri, Simuka, uende kubani, ndichataura newe ipapo.
\p
\v 23 Zvino ndakasimuka, ndikaenda kubani, ndikaona kubwinya kwaJehovha kumirepo, kwakafanana nokubwinya kwandakaona parwizi rwaKebhari; ndikawira pasi nechiso changu.
\v 24 Ipapo Mweya wakapinda mandiri, ukandimisa namakumbo angu, ukataura neni, ukati kwandiri, Enda, undozvipfigira mumba mako.
\v 25 Asi iwe, Mwanakomana womunhu, tarira, vachauya nezvisungo kwauri, vachakusunga nazvo, kuti urege kubudira pakati pavo;
\v 26 ini ndichanamatirisa rurimi rwako mumukamwa wako, kuti uve mbeveve, urege kuva murayiri wavo; nokuti ivo iimba inondimukira simba.
\v 27 Asi kana ndichitaura newe, ndichashamisa muromo wako, iwe ugoti kwavari, `Zvanzi nalshe Jehovha, anonzwa ngaanzwe, anoramba, ngaarambe; nokuti ivo iimba inondimukira simba.'
